{"word":"G592 - ἀποδιορίζω - apodiorízō - ap-od-ee-or-id'-zo - Separate","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀποδιορίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apodiorízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-od-ee-or-id'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Separate</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பிரிந்துபோ"},{"paragraph":"by drawing boundaries to disjoin, part, separate from another"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and a compound of <a href=\"#/G1223 - διά - diá - dee-ah'/1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G3724 - ὁρίζω - horízō - hor-id'-zo/3724\">G3724</a>; to <i>disjoin</i> (by a boundary, figuratively a party): - separate.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3724/3724\">G3724</a>, <a href=\"#/G4309/4309\">G4309</a>, <a href=\"#/G592/592\">G592</a>, <a href=\"#/G873/873\">G873</a>"}]}